{"tid":1684163,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實係呢場運動/革命 連登仔女知唔知自己嘅崗位係邊？","createTime":"2019-10-31T03:13:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T03:40:54.000Z","uid":311193,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6d44f0214c9cb2a6f87dc611f97e9c675c1fca83","tid":1684163,"uid":311193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:13:04.000Z","msg":"又係我啦 我係唔會放棄 直到連登回復正常 3個月前嘅連登只係會做號召力 依家個個都做偵探 分析又話勇武唔應該參加大遊行 唔應該去港島 其實最自打嘴巴係連登仔女 又話和勇合一 但勇武唔好去 呢幾日一定會狂吹風話分區搞 又話唔好有勇武出席 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>但係其實冇勇武係會再睇連登</strong></span></span> 612阻止二讀 71衝入立法會令成個立法會開唔到會議 依家成個世界各地都關注香港 都係因為勇武嘅勇敢同犧牲 連登仔女呀 其實最冇資格講嘢係你哋 勇武做咁多嘢 付出咁多 一直俾你哋用匿名係網上講個樣做得唔好呢樣要點做先岩 又叫勇武休息 其實你哋係最應該聽勇武嘅指示 唔該最後幾日 <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><del>連登仔女做返自己職責啦 連登係號召力嘅地方 淨係做聚人嘅崗位呀唔該</del></span></span></strong><br />\n611晚係人都知出咗去添馬一定係高危 但個個都照出 9成嘅號召力係連登仔女嘅文宣 但點解會咁多人出 點解會又有和勇出現 係因為連登冇過份去分析個一晚會點 大家係知高危 但大家都不顧後果去阻止二讀 話強權製造白色恐怖 但其實連登嘅分析就已經係為自己手足製造咗恐懼 <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我想講嘅係 大家可唔可以一人少一句分析 反而多返多啲號召力同文宣呢？</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">112維園見</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最後最後</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uehiWdP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuehiWdP.jpg&h=22080ca9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8iyaNku.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8iyaNku.jpg&h=d61b7bef&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KKAc0Fw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKKAc0Fw.jpg&h=00653d56&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LA1DbNb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLA1DbNb.gif&h=8faaa07a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3cdx0Fx.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3cdx0Fx.gif&h=8d99743e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6d25f8c9c23881c62c5e5dc80e61421908ec88b5","tid":1684163,"uid":311193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:13:55.000Z","msg":"1連推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n112 維園見"},{"pid":"03231fe2a7f2bb0bd652452164cc33d5dd27330a","tid":1684163,"uid":311193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:14:17.000Z","msg":"2連推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n112 維園見"},{"pid":"8c4cc85705580c4b252ac80dc860c61f04236c00","tid":1684163,"uid":311193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:14:43.000Z","msg":"3連推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n112維園見"},{"pid":"27708be64c7da4cf1106baffeb10063b25b63ecb","tid":1684163,"uid":311193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:15:45.000Z","msg":"4連推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n112 維園見"},{"pid":"3943e9e493fa751155dbc6dcfb6e1057bbb527bc","tid":1684163,"uid":311193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:16:17.000Z","msg":"5連推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n112 維園見"},{"pid":"389f188849fe419575c3afc83bb620472d8f66c4","tid":1684163,"uid":311193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:16:51.000Z","msg":"推上熱門"},{"pid":"a12b6ef9029005e40f1ad175175801cdb049aec3","tid":1684163,"uid":311193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:17:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n112維園眼"},{"pid":"66bfaebe650ef087e59ea279f14f246284610f91","tid":1684163,"uid":311193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:17:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n112維園見</blockquote>"},{"pid":"084603d5fa947766785645d522548875f6329e1a","tid":1684163,"uid":311193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:17:35.000Z","msg":"112維園見"},{"pid":"8b2318fc2fd7ca73a1cd401d00b9b001ce4c6ff3","tid":1684163,"uid":311193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:22:16.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"cba511e570a8afe19c7709bd09bed7cb4c8ffa5a","tid":1684163,"uid":311193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:22:35.000Z","msg":"112行動post要上熱門呀"},{"pid":"aedb4348ecf8a86f6fa3cf5be305f9fc6da6ae87","tid":1684163,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:40:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樹窿再次歡迎大家加入<br />\n知道過去兩個月，大家既生活都過得好壓抑。有人係依兩個月之間同父母嗌大交，同伴侶分手，同朋友斷交，有人晚晚夜歸，有人用到無哂錢。或者你覺得好迷惘好無奈，或者你覺得無岀路。有見及此，開左個谷俾大家入黎吐下苦水，只談現實，不談夢境。希望大家可以舒發下，減減壓，然後大家一齊繼續向前行。<br />\n<br />\n發緊想發未發就發夢都唔好係公海講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保障大家安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講明先 係歡迎任何人講既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n理得你藍定黃 狗定人 貓定兔<br />\n我地好希望大家可以有個好始既渠道釋放咁耐以來既情緒<br />\n如果大家有朋友仔想入來都無任歡迎咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋記得不指責不要質問 任何指責及質問均無助大家發洩情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nlink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/ourtreehole\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fourtreehole&d=N2LCmr%2FexNvWBpgyITFnA%2F7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=f5d8673a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ourtreehole</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無論你係邊一到，保護自己，不要透露個人資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人，反抗！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}